<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="relate-v">relate <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /rɪ'leɪt/    美 /rɪ'leɪt/  </p>
<p>[常与to连用]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-connect">1.★ <strong>(使) 互有关联 (connect)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The report seeks to <strong>relate</strong> the rise in crime to an increase in unemployment<strong>to_2</strong>
这篇报告试图证明犯罪活动的增加与失业率的上涨有关。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The second paragraph <strong>relates to</strong> the trade war between US and China.
第二段涉及到了中美之间的贸易战。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>[正式用语] 叙述；讲：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He related how the accident happened. 
他叙述了事故发生的经过。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>理解；认同：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I love technology and try to keep up with it so I can <strong>relate to</strong> my students.  
我热爱技术，并试图跟上技术的发展，因此我可以理解学生的想法。</p><footer>2011 北京</footer></div></div>